{"tid":898894,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"廣島旅遊求指教","createTime":"2018-11-12T04:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T09:08:34.000Z","uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"96d34ddea1fe9c6788f1bc8e067820ca704482e0","tid":898894,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"我計劃出年9月去廣島，約莫6日5夜/5日4夜<br />\n想請教以下行程怕唔怕太趕？<br />\n<br />\n第一日：落機、去廣島市遊覽<br />\n第二日：宮島神社、錦帶橋、返廣島<br />\n第三日：大久野島、尾道<br />\n第四日：踩車去今治市，再返回尾道<br />\n第五日：留守廣島<br />\n第六日：返歸<br />\n<br />\n請問我呢個行程會否太趕？<br />\n想請教下各位意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0b3bc1fdc47ea56b30910524624dc18e4b155a","tid":898894,"uid":35502,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:35:16.000Z","msg":"大久野島一定要早起身出發"},{"pid":"c85a36ab3fc5903a80aca7084ebe31bc288f2976","tid":898894,"uid":35502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc0b3bc1fdc47ea56b30910524624dc18e4b155a","tid":898894,"uid":35502,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:35:16.000Z","msg":"大久野島一定要早起身出發"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:37:37.000Z","msg":"可以前一日係超市買定d菜 平過上船前買好多 記住洗乾淨無水先餵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981aec07670ff079a9d74b3377f48415bc8e1248","tid":898894,"uid":15880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:28:15.000Z","msg":"錦帶橋伏伏地冇咩睇<br />\n宮島留耐d / 過夜仲好"},{"pid":"9d7e444d1ea42b4a1c5d372c7b05746e18fcd223","tid":898894,"uid":8934,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"981aec07670ff079a9d74b3377f48415bc8e1248","tid":898894,"uid":15880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:28:15.000Z","msg":"錦帶橋伏伏地冇咩睇<br />\n宮島留耐d / 過夜仲好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05